{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"♫ Jill Sobule: At a conference in Monterey by the big, big jellyfish tank, ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"♫ I first saw you and I got so shy. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23000,"text":"♫ You see, I was a little paranoid 'cause I might have been high. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"♫ And I hadn't done that in ages and I won't do that again. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"♫ But that's another story. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"♫ Loved you forever and I've been a big fan, ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"♫ the one-woman shows, I even rented \"Pat.\" ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"♫ I got enough nerve to come up to you, ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"♫ but little did I know one year later we'd be doing this show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"♫ I sing. Julia Sweeney: I tell stories. Together: The Jill and Julia Show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Sometimes it works. Sweeney: Sometimes it doesn't. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"♫ Together: The Jill and Julia Show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"♫ Sweeney: At a conference in Monterey next to the big, big jellyfish tank, ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"♫ I first saw you and I wasn't so shy. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"I made a beeline for you and told you what a huge fan I was"},{"time":79000,"text":"ever since I was writing that pilot for Fox, and Wendy"},{"time":82000,"text":"and I wanted you to do the theme song."},{"time":83000,"text":"And then the pilot didn't go and I was so sad,"},{"time":85000,"text":"but I kept remaining a fan of yours."},{"time":86000,"text":"And then when I went through that big, horrible breakup with Carl"},{"time":90000,"text":"and I couldn't get off the couch, I listened to your song,"},{"time":92000,"text":"♫ \"Now That I Don't Have You,\" ♫ over and over and over and over again."},{"time":96000,"text":"And I can't believe you're here and that I'm meeting you here at TED."},{"time":99000,"text":"And also, I can't believe that we're eating sushi"},{"time":102000,"text":"in front of the fish tank,"},{"time":103000,"text":"which, personally, I think is really inappropriate."},{"time":105000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":107000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":108000,"text":"And little did I know that one year later ... ♫ we'd be doing this show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112000,"text":"♫ Sobule: I sing. Sweeney: I tell stories. Together: The Jill and Julia Show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"Sobule: Hey, they asked us back! Sweeney: Can you stand it?!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"♫ Together: The Jill and Julia, the Jill and Julia, the Jill and Julia Show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Why are all our heroes so imperfect? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"♫ Why do they always bring me down? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"♫ Why are all our heroes so imperfect? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":147000,"text":"♫ Statue in the park has lost his crown. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"♫ William Faulkner, drunk and depressed. ♫ Sweeney: Mmm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"♫ Dorothy Parker, mean, drunk and depressed. ♫ Sweeney: I know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"♫ And that guy, \"Seven Years in Tibet,\" turned out to be a Nazi. ♫ Sweeney: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"♫ Founding fathers all had slaves. ♫ Sweeney: I know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165000,"text":"♫ The explorers slaughtered the braves. ♫ Sweeney: Horribly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168000,"text":"♫ Sobule: The Old Testament God can be so petty. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"Sweeney: Don't get me started on that. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Paul McCartney, jealous of John, even more so now that he's gone. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"♫ Dylan was so mean to Donovan in that movie. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183000,"text":"♫ Pablo Picasso, cruel to his wives. ♫ Sweeney: Horrible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"♫ Sobule: My favorite poets took their own lives. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"♫ Orson Welles peaked at twenty-five, below before our eyes. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"♫ And he sold bad wine. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":195000,"text":"♫ Together: Why are all our heroes so imperfect? Yeah ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"♫ Why do they always bring me down? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Heard Babe Ruth was full of malice. ♫ Sweeney: Oh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208000,"text":"♫ Lewis Carroll I'm sure did Alice. ♫ Sweeney: What?!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"♫ Plato in the cave with those very young boys. ♫ Sweeney: Ooh..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Hillary supported the war. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"♫ Sweeney: Even Thomas Friedman supported the war. ♫ (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Colin Powell turned out to be ... Together: ... such a pussy. ♫ (Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"♫ Sobule: William Faulkner, drunk and depressed, ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"♫ Tennessee Williams, drunk and depressed. ♫ Sweeney: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Take it, Julia. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"Sweeney: Okay. Oprah was never necessarily a big hero of mine."},{"time":236000,"text":"I mean, I watch Oprah mostly when I'm home in Spokane"},{"time":239000,"text":"visiting my mother. And to my mother,"},{"time":241000,"text":"Oprah is a greater moral authority than the Pope,"},{"time":243000,"text":"which is actually saying something because she's a devout Catholic."},{"time":246000,"text":"Anyway, I like Oprah -- I like her girlfriendy-ness,"},{"time":249000,"text":"I like her weight issues,"},{"time":251000,"text":"I like how she's transformed talk television,"},{"time":253000,"text":"I like how she's brought reading back to America --"},{"time":256000,"text":"but there was something that happened the last two weeks"},{"time":258000,"text":"that was ... I call it the Soon-Yi moment:"},{"time":261000,"text":"it is the moment when I cannot continue supporting someone."},{"time":266000,"text":"And that was that she did two entire shows"},{"time":270000,"text":"promoting that movie \"The Secret.\""},{"time":272000,"text":"Do you guys know about that movie \"The Secret\"?"},{"time":274000,"text":"It makes \"What the Bleep Do We Know\" seem like a doctoral dissertation"},{"time":279000,"text":"from Harvard on quantum mechanics -- that's how bad it is."},{"time":282000,"text":"It makes \"The DaVinci Code\" seem like \"War and Peace.\""},{"time":286000,"text":"That movie is so horrible. It promotes such awful pseudoscience."},{"time":291000,"text":"And the basic idea is"},{"time":292000,"text":"that there's this law of attraction, and"},{"time":295000,"text":"your thoughts have this vibrating energy"},{"time":297000,"text":"that goes out into the universe"},{"time":298000,"text":"and then you attract good things to happen to you."},{"time":300000,"text":"On a scientific basis, it's more than just \"Power of Positive Thinking\" --"},{"time":304000,"text":"it has a horrible, horrible dark side. Like if you get ill,"},{"time":309000,"text":"it's because you've just been thinking negative thoughts."},{"time":311000,"text":"Yeah, stuff like that was in the movie and she's promoting it."},{"time":314000,"text":"And all I'm saying is that I really wish that Murray Gell-Mann"},{"time":317000,"text":"would go on Oprah"},{"time":318000,"text":"and just explain to her that the law of attraction is, in fact, not a law."},{"time":323000,"text":"So that's what I have to say."},{"time":325000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333000,"text":"♫ Sobule: I sing. Sweeney: I tell stories. Together: The Jill and Julia Show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"♫ Sobule: Sometimes it works. Sweeney: Sometimes it doesn't. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"♫ Together: The Jill and Julia, the Jill and Julia, the Jill and Julia Show. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}